org.dcm4che3.conf.core.api

Annotation Type ConfigurableProperty


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface ConfigurableProperty
    Marks a field of a configuration class to be a persistable configuration property of the bean
    Author:
    Roman K

      • weakReference

        public abstract boolean weakReference
        Only affects behavior for references. Indicates that the frameworks should not prevent removal of the target of this reference from the configuration. For a reference for which it was detected that the target does not exist anymore, the value gets automatically removed on occasion, i.e. will be set to 'null'
        Returns:
        Default:
        false
